<h2>Sugestii, propuneri pentru DentistOnline</h2>
<div class='clearfix'></div>
<form class="form-horizontal" role="form" action="" method='post'>
<div class='row well well-lg login_form'>
	<div class="help-block text-left">
		Daca aveti sugestii sau propuneri pentru noi, pe diverse teme cum ar fi: <u>subiecte de articole</u> dorite, <u>imbunatatiri</u> servicii DentistOnline, va rugam nu ezitati sa le aduceti la cunostinta noastra.
		<br><br>Va multumim si va spunem <b>"PAREREA TA E IMPORTANTA"</b> .
	</div>
	<div class='col-xs-12 text-center'>
		<div class="form-group form-group-lg">
			<div class="input-group">
				<div class="input-group-addon" id='name'><span class='glyphicon glyphicon-pencil'></span></div>
				<input type="text" name='name' class="form-control" placeholder="Nume / Prenume ..." value="{NAME}" aria-describedby="name">
			</div>
		</div>
		<div class="form-group form-group-lg">
			<div class="input-group">
				<div class="input-group-addon" id='email'><span class='glyphicon glyphicon-envelope'></span></div>
				<input type="text" name='email' class="form-control" placeholder="Adresa de email ..." value="{EMAIL}" aria-describedby="email">
			</div>
		</div>
		<div class="form-group form-group-lg">
			<div class="input-group col-xs-12">
				<textarea name='text' class="form-control" placeholder="Scrieti aici sugestiile dvs ..." rows='10'>{TEXT}</textarea>
			</div>
		</div>
		
		<div class="form-group form-group-lg">
			<div class="input-group col-xs-12">
				<div class="input-group-addon" id='security'><img src="{SITE_BASE}/security_image.php?code={SECURITYID}" alt="Security Image"></div>
				<input type="text" name="security_code" class="form-control" placeholder="Cod securitate..." value="" aria-describedby="security">
			</div>
		</div>
		<div class="form-group form-group-lg">
			<div class="input-group col-xs-12 text-left">
				<button type="submit" name="send" class="btn btn-info btn-lg">Trimite</button>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</div>
</form>
